dismissalText.commentary: Harry Brook c Jansen b Maharaj 19 (29b 3x4 0x6 43m) SR: 65.51

dismissalComment.html: wondercatch at deep midwicket! Angling into Brook's arc, and he looks to belt Maharaj over midwicket. He nearly gets away with it, the breeze carrying the ball towards the boundary as it hung in the air, but Jansen keeps on chasing after it and takes a blinder. He ran around a long way from long-on, dived to his right, and slid onto his knees and he got it. Covered 28 metres per the TV broadcast
